1
00:00:03,867 --> 00:00:05,267
Come on, Yuhao.

2
00:00:05,367 --> 00:00:07,066
Although I don't hold much hope...

3
00:00:07,333 --> 00:00:10,266
Let me see just how far you can go.

4
00:00:21,333 --> 00:00:23,366
Seeing how the Tang Sect has developed...

5
00:00:23,700 --> 00:00:24,999
I'm truly happy.

6
00:00:25,233 --> 00:00:26,899
With the medicinal effect of the
Qiankun Creation Pill...

7
00:00:27,367 --> 00:00:29,632
Extending Teacher Xiaoya's life by three years
shouldn't be a problem.

8
00:01:49,467 --> 00:01:52,766
The Qiankun Creation Pill helped Wutong
successfully break through the level 90 bottleneck.

9
00:01:53,233 --> 00:01:55,132
She's just one soul ring away
from becoming a Title Douluo.

10
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:04,532
Wutong, have you decided on your title yet?

11
00:02:06,700 --> 00:02:08,032
I decided long ago.

12
00:02:15,867 --> 00:02:16,867
My title...

13
00:02:18,233 --> 00:02:19,233
Will be Dragon Butterfly.

14
00:02:22,767 --> 00:02:24,566
Dragon Butterfly... what a fine name.

15
00:02:25,900 --> 00:02:27,232
Congratulations, Wutong.

16
00:02:28,667 --> 00:02:30,132
Not long ago, Teacher Xuan also broke through.

17
00:02:30,967 --> 00:02:33,199
Senior Brother Ji's cultivation has reached level 89 as well.

18
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:36,432
Yuhao, you can't fall behind now.

19
00:02:36,967 --> 00:02:38,832
You've been stuck at the level 89 bottleneck
for quite a while, haven't you?

20
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:41,899
It's my own fault for condensing my first soul core
too early.

21
00:02:42,300 --> 00:02:44,566
It made breaking through to Title Douluo
much more difficult.

22
00:02:45,067 --> 00:02:45,499
Yuhao.

23
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:47,499
Senior Brother.

24
00:02:48,900 --> 00:02:50,899
Yuhao, the academy wants you to come over.

25
00:02:51,533 --> 00:02:53,132
Apparently Elder Xuan and the others
have come out of seclusion.

26
00:02:53,767 --> 00:02:54,767
Elder Xuan has come out of seclusion?

27
00:03:00,433 --> 00:03:01,999
Elder Xuan, you've broken through!

28
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:06,566
I finally broke through that barrier.
It really wasn't easy.

29
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:10,599
This bottleneck had troubled me for countless years.

30
00:03:11,300 --> 00:03:13,966
Breaking through in a single stroke
feels like being reborn.

31
00:03:14,900 --> 00:03:16,166
Congratulations, Elder Xuan.

32
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:17,600
It's not just me.

33
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:19,866
The Qiankun Creation Pill you sent...

34
00:03:20,033 --> 00:03:23,332
Also helped Shaozhe and Lin'er break through
their current bottlenecks.

35
00:03:23,767 --> 00:03:26,099
Their soul power increased by one level.

36
00:03:26,733 --> 00:03:28,132
Thank you, Yuhao.

37
00:03:28,833 --> 00:03:30,866
Beibei, Yuhao, Wutong...

38
00:03:31,300 --> 00:03:34,532
The reason I called you here today
is for another extremely important matter.

39
00:03:35,033 --> 00:03:39,599
A few days ago, the Heavenly Soul Empire,
Dou Ling Empire, and Star Luo Empire
simultaneously sent envoys to our academy.

40
00:03:40,167 --> 00:03:43,699
They hope we can lend a hand
and take part in a secret operation.

41
00:03:44,367 --> 00:03:45,367
A secret operation?

42
00:03:46,067 --> 00:03:47,699
To assassinate Xu Tianran.

43
00:03:51,467 --> 00:03:53,766
The current situation on the continent
is turbulent and unpredictable.

44
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:56,932
Although the Sun Moon Empire
hasn't expanded the war for now...

45
00:03:57,433 --> 00:04:01,099
They've deployed a large number of
high-altitude surveillance soul tools
along the border.

46
00:04:02,100 --> 00:04:06,599
All the signs point to them preparing
for an even larger war.

47
00:04:10,833 --> 00:04:12,999
At this moment,
launching a decapitation strike against
the Sun Moon Empire...

48
00:04:13,333 --> 00:04:14,932
Is the most economical and effective method.

49
00:04:15,967 --> 00:04:20,166
And once Xu Tianran falls,
the Sun Moon Empire will inevitably fall
into long-term chaos.

50
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:23,232
For the Heavenly Soul, Dou Ling,
and Star Luo Empires...

51
00:04:23,567 --> 00:04:25,732
Ending the war in one fell swoop
might not be impossible.

52
00:04:26,933 --> 00:04:27,899
It's too risky.

53
00:04:28,433 --> 00:04:31,932
As emperor, Xu Tianran is sure to be protected
by a large number of top experts.

54
00:04:32,667 --> 00:04:35,399
And he himself is a Title Douluo-level powerhouse.

55
00:04:36,667 --> 00:04:39,999
Although the original three empires of the Douluo Continent
have always stood together with Shrek Academy...

56
00:04:40,867 --> 00:04:42,466
For us to join such a risky and aggressive operation...

57
00:04:42,867 --> 00:04:44,732
If Shrek is to participate as well...

58
00:04:45,367 --> 00:04:49,766
We're not asking you to join directly.
The envoys from the three empires
only have one request.

59
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:51,732
Assistance.

60
00:04:53,067 --> 00:04:55,566
For this operation,
Yuhao's Spiritual Detection Sharing...

61
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:55,899
Yuhao's Spiritual Detection Sharing...

62
00:04:55,900 --> 00:04:57,666
Is the support ability they need most.

63
00:04:58,900 --> 00:05:03,366
With this ability, the chances of the operation
succeeding will increase dramatically.

64
00:05:05,500 --> 00:05:07,532
Alright, I accept. I'll go with them.

65
00:05:07,833 --> 00:05:08,833
Yuhao...

66
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:11,366
As Dean Xian said,
assassinating Xu Tianran...

67
00:05:11,733 --> 00:05:14,432
Is indeed the most economical way
to prevent the war from expanding right now.

68
00:05:15,533 --> 00:05:17,132
That man is cunning and paranoid by nature.

69
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:21,166
He played a decisive role
in the Sun Moon Empire launching wars abroad.

70
00:05:22,133 --> 00:05:23,166
If we can eliminate him...

71
00:05:23,667 --> 00:05:26,499
The Sun Moon Empire's war machine
will very likely grind to a halt.

72
00:05:27,067 --> 00:05:29,232
Besides, I've been stuck at the level 89 bottleneck
for a long time too.

73
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:31,832
I need real combat experience
to find an opportunity to break through.

74
00:05:33,433 --> 00:05:34,832
Then the seven of us Shrek Monsters
should go together.

75
00:05:35,267 --> 00:05:36,866
We seven are one. We live and die together.

76
00:05:38,367 --> 00:05:41,599
No. This operation is extremely confidential.

77
00:05:42,500 --> 00:05:46,632
If all seven Shrek Monsters move out together,
the number of people would be too many.
It wouldn't be appropriate.

78
00:05:47,533 --> 00:05:49,366
Senior Brother, thank you for your kindness.

79
00:05:50,267 --> 00:05:52,432
Don't worry. I'll definitely return safely.

80
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:56,732
Alright... you must come back safe and sound.

81
00:05:57,100 --> 00:05:57,532
Yuhao...

82
00:05:58,300 --> 00:05:59,266
I'll go with you.

83
00:06:00,533 --> 00:06:01,999
No, it's too dangerous.

84
00:06:03,167 --> 00:06:06,032
My cultivation isn't below yours,
and I have ways to protect myself.

85
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:10,032
Didn't we agree that we'd face
anything together?

86
00:06:12,033 --> 00:06:13,033
Fine.

87
00:06:13,633 --> 00:06:16,132
We'll discuss the specific action plan later.

88
00:06:16,467 --> 00:06:18,999
Yuhao, Wutong, come with me.

89
00:06:23,067 --> 00:06:27,032
The most important step in breaking through
to Title Douluo is condensing a soul core.

90
00:06:28,233 --> 00:06:32,066
Yuhao, you condensed your first soul core
very early, back when you were still a Soul Saint.

91
00:06:32,867 --> 00:06:36,366
So the difficulty of condensing a second soul core
is easy to imagine.

92
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:40,599
And if you wish to charge toward
Limit Douluo in the future...

93
00:06:40,900 --> 00:06:44,399
You may even need to condense
a never-before-seen third soul core.

94
00:06:44,867 --> 00:06:47,566
If only I hadn't condensed my first soul core
so early...

95
00:06:49,433 --> 00:06:51,766
No. That step wasn't a mistake.

96
00:06:52,733 --> 00:06:55,199
Condensing your first soul core
during the Soul Saint stage...

97
00:06:55,400 --> 00:06:57,932
Has made your soul power
extraordinarily solid.

98
00:06:58,900 --> 00:07:00,799
If you successfully condense
a second soul core...

99
00:07:00,933 --> 00:07:03,799
Your strength will far surpass
that of an ordinary Title Douluo.

100
00:07:04,233 --> 00:07:05,899
Directly reaching the level of a Super Douluo.

101
00:07:05,900 --> 00:07:06,900
Directly reaching the level of a Super Douluo.

102
00:07:07,533 --> 00:07:10,232
And on that foundation,
if you condense a third soul core...

103
00:07:10,633 --> 00:07:13,566
No one on the entire Douluo Continent
will be your match.

104
00:07:14,167 --> 00:07:15,699
Not even a Limit Douluo.

105
00:07:18,067 --> 00:07:20,199
This time, when I successfully broke through
to Limit Douluo...

106
00:07:20,500 --> 00:07:22,732
I gained a much deeper understanding of soul cores.

107
00:07:23,567 --> 00:07:27,166
Listen carefully. I'm sure it will help you.

108
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:29,200
Thank you, Elder Xuan.

109
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:34,666
The first soul core is an extreme compression
of your soul power...

110
00:07:34,867 --> 00:07:39,032
To achieve a qualitative leap,
making it the core of your soul power.

111
00:07:39,967 --> 00:07:43,132
The second soul core, however,
is completely different from the first.

112
00:07:43,833 --> 00:07:45,632
Because when you condense the second soul core...

113
00:07:45,867 --> 00:07:48,599
The first soul core has already become
the core of your soul power.

114
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:52,332
The second soul core will inevitably
interact with it.

115
00:07:53,233 --> 00:07:58,499
The slightest carelessness could cause the two soul cores
to collide, leading to your body exploding.

116
00:07:59,567 --> 00:08:03,532
Back then, the method Elder Mu taught me
for condensing the second soul core...

117
00:08:03,667 --> 00:08:05,466
Was called homotopic resonance.

118
00:08:06,133 --> 00:08:10,032
Simply put, the second soul core
submits to the first soul core...

119
00:08:10,467 --> 00:08:12,332
And revolves around it.

120
00:08:12,933 --> 00:08:16,966
That way, the second soul core
will inevitably be much smaller than the first.

121
00:08:18,933 --> 00:08:19,933
Correct.

122
00:08:20,033 --> 00:08:24,132
Therefore, anyone who condenses their second soul core
using the homotopic resonance method...

123
00:08:24,433 --> 00:08:27,032
Will never be able to condense a third soul core.

124
00:08:27,833 --> 00:08:30,866
Yuhao, what I'm about to tell you now...

125
00:08:31,333 --> 00:08:33,932
Is another method to condense the second soul core.

126
00:08:34,967 --> 00:08:36,532
Yin-Yang complementarity.

127
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:38,199
Yin-Yang complementarity?

128
00:08:40,300 --> 00:08:41,666
The so-called yin-yang complementarity...

129
00:08:42,467 --> 00:08:47,232
Means the two soul cores depend on each other
and revolve around one another.

130
00:08:48,933 --> 00:08:51,266
A second soul core condensed this way...

131
00:08:51,533 --> 00:08:53,699
Will be far stronger than one formed
through homotopic resonance.

132
00:08:54,167 --> 00:08:58,032
At the same time, the condensation process
is also much more dangerous.

133
00:08:59,233 --> 00:09:00,233
Please teach me, Elder Xuan.

134
00:09:00,257 --> 00:09:17,357
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

135
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:21,532
Using this method to condense the second soul core...

136
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:26,199
You must completely resist the attractive force
of the first soul core during the process.

137
00:09:26,833 --> 00:09:28,599
It will require tremendous willpower.

138
00:09:29,133 --> 00:09:33,666
Furthermore, the total soul power of the second soul core
must be exactly the same as the first.

139
00:09:34,400 --> 00:09:39,166
At the same time, the rotation direction of the second soul core
must be completely opposite to the first.

140
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:43,666
Ultimately forming an extreme balance
of yin-yang complementarity.

141
00:09:44,967 --> 00:09:49,199
Elder Xuan, does the Beast God Di Tian
have yin-yang complementary dual soul cores?

142
00:09:50,633 --> 00:09:55,299
Very good. It seems you already have
some understanding of yin-yang complementarity.

143
00:09:57,067 --> 00:10:00,699
Di Tian indeed possesses yin-yang complementary dual soul cores.

144
00:10:01,133 --> 00:10:04,966
The reason he succeeded
is because his physical body is strong enough...

145
00:10:05,333 --> 00:10:07,732
To withstand the extreme pulling force
from the first soul core...

146
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:09,832
During the condensation of the second.

147
00:10:10,433 --> 00:10:13,199
At the same time, his lifespan is long enough...

148
00:10:13,767 --> 00:10:17,099
To allow him to slowly accumulate
the second soul core over a long period.

149
00:10:17,933 --> 00:10:20,732
And it is precisely because his soul cores
are yin-yang complementary...

150
00:10:21,233 --> 00:10:24,166
That Long Xiaoyao and Ye Xishui
are not his match.

151
00:10:24,833 --> 00:10:27,132
Even if the two of them join forces.

152
00:10:28,100 --> 00:10:30,732
Even two Limit Douluos working together
are no match for Di Tian.

153
00:10:31,133 --> 00:10:32,432
Di Tian is actually that powerful?

154
00:10:33,800 --> 00:10:34,732
Regrettably...

155
00:10:35,133 --> 00:10:38,199
Di Tian’s cultivation method
cannot be applied to you.

156
00:10:39,067 --> 00:10:41,632
You don’t possess his supreme bloodline
or his powerful physique.

157
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:44,099
Nor do you have his extraordinarily long lifespan.

158
00:10:45,033 --> 00:10:47,666
You must comprehend your own path.

159
00:10:48,900 --> 00:10:49,966
I will definitely succeed.

160
00:10:51,267 --> 00:10:52,267
And...

161
00:10:53,367 --> 00:10:54,367
With three soul cores.

162
00:11:08,433 --> 00:11:09,899
That is the main peak of the Ming Dou Mountain Range.

163
00:11:12,900 --> 00:11:15,966
Back when Ye Xishui fought Di Tian,
their battle shook heaven and earth.

164
00:11:17,100 --> 00:11:18,599
The majestic main peak of the Ming Dou Mountain Range...

165
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:21,166
Was leveled flat by the mere shockwaves
of their fight.

166
00:11:22,767 --> 00:11:26,432
Now this place has become
the location of the White Tiger Duke’s command tent.

167
00:11:28,933 --> 00:11:30,266
I’m going to see that person again...

168
00:11:34,467 --> 00:11:36,366
Yuhao, you seem a little nervous.

169
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,200
Do I?

170
00:11:44,933 --> 00:11:46,132
Benefactor, you’ve arrived.

171
00:11:47,567 --> 00:11:48,632
General Zhang, there’s no need for such formality.

172
00:11:49,367 --> 00:11:51,832
The Marshal and the Title Douluos
have been waiting in the tent for quite some time.

173
00:11:52,300 --> 00:11:53,300
Please, come in.

174
00:12:02,267 --> 00:12:03,267
Yuhao...

175
00:12:14,833 --> 00:12:16,632
Yuhao, you’re here.

176
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:19,699
You must be Tang Wutong.

177
00:12:20,967 --> 00:12:21,999
Greetings, Your Grace.

178
00:12:23,700 --> 00:12:26,299
Wutong has already advanced to Title Douluo.
Her title is Dragon Butterfly.

179
00:12:26,900 --> 00:12:28,332
Her strength is actually above mine.

180
00:12:37,833 --> 00:12:40,166
You’ve finally come to see your father.
That’s wonderful.

181
00:12:40,467 --> 00:12:40,766
Du— Brother...

182
00:12:41,367 --> 00:12:42,367
What is it?

183
00:12:42,567 --> 00:12:44,632
In the army, we address people by their position.

184
00:12:45,233 --> 00:12:46,233
It’s “Regiment Commander.”

185
00:12:47,133 --> 00:12:48,899
Senior Dai, long time no see.

186
00:12:49,667 --> 00:12:51,099
Welcome, Junior Brother Huo.

187
00:12:51,500 --> 00:12:54,899
What formidable soul power.
I’ve already reached Soul Douluo level...

188
00:12:55,067 --> 00:12:57,099
And I’m even more outstanding
than my father was at my age.

189
00:12:57,367 --> 00:13:00,532
But compared to Huo Yuhao,
I still can’t compare.

190
00:13:00,967 --> 00:13:03,232
And he’s a full seven years younger than me.

191
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:06,399
Brother...

192
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:12,299
Come, let me introduce everyone.

193
00:13:14,333 --> 00:13:17,132
This is the outstanding genius
from Shrek Academy...

194
00:13:17,567 --> 00:13:19,566
Huo Yuhao, the Eye of the Asura.

195
00:13:21,367 --> 00:13:24,299
Don’t let his young age fool you.
He helped us tremendously back then.

196
00:13:25,300 --> 00:13:30,099
Without him, Star Luo might never have
been able to reclaim the Ming Dou Mountain Range.

197
00:13:30,967 --> 00:13:33,066
Truly a hero from a young age.

198
00:13:36,833 --> 00:13:37,833
Senior Poison...

199
00:13:39,767 --> 00:13:44,199
How come Senior Du’s cultivation has dropped
slightly compared to when he fought Di Tian?

200
00:13:45,533 --> 00:13:48,399
It seems the losses suffered by the Body Sect
were even more severe than expected.

201
00:13:49,933 --> 00:13:52,566
Half of the Title Douluos here
are Super Douluos.

202
00:13:53,967 --> 00:13:58,699
This one’s cultivation is as high as level 97,
second only to Senior Poison.

203
00:14:00,667 --> 00:14:02,032
Reclaiming the Ming Dou Mountain Range...

204
00:14:02,300 --> 00:14:04,599
Naturally, the Duke deserves the greatest credit.

205
00:14:04,967 --> 00:14:07,899
I wouldn’t dare take the credit.
Yuhao, come.

206
00:14:08,100 --> 00:14:11,866
Let me introduce you.
This is the Heavenly Sun Douluo from the Dou Ling Empire.

207
00:14:12,900 --> 00:14:14,766
Senior Heavenly Sun is over 150 years old.

208
00:14:15,267 --> 00:14:16,732
He’s a senior figure in the soul master world.

209
00:14:17,500 --> 00:14:20,699
A level 97 Super Douluo
with extremely formidable strength.

210
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:25,599
This operation will be led by
Senior Body Sect and Senior Heavenly Sun.

211
00:14:28,033 --> 00:14:29,599
Greetings, Senior Heavenly Sun.

212
00:14:30,900 --> 00:14:32,566
A promising young talent indeed.

213
00:14:53,300 --> 00:14:54,799
Level 89 soul power...

214
00:14:58,433 --> 00:15:00,332
The younger generation is truly formidable.

215
00:15:01,867 --> 00:15:06,432
We old folks really are about to step off
the stage of history.

216
00:15:07,100 --> 00:15:10,866
Since everyone is here,
let’s discuss the operation plan first.

217
00:15:11,433 --> 00:15:13,132
Dai Hao, you explain.

218
00:15:15,133 --> 00:15:17,566
For this operation,
our Star Luo Empire...

219
00:15:17,567 --> 00:15:21,766
Along with the Heavenly Soul Empire and Dou Ling Empire,
will each contribute five Title Douluos.

220
00:15:22,300 --> 00:15:23,866
We will head to the Sun Moon Empire together...

221
00:15:24,267 --> 00:15:27,099
To carry out the assassination
of the Sun Moon Empire’s emperor, Xu Tianran.

222
00:15:27,933 --> 00:15:30,466
The operation is codenamed:
Emperor Extinction.

223
00:15:32,448 --> 00:15:39,512
[Tang Wutong — Titled Douluo]

224
00:15:39,536 --> 00:15:46,992
[Sun Douluo - Debut Level: Level 97 - As the foremost offering priest of the Spirit Hall, he possesses top-tier strength among Super Douluo. His martial soul, Sun, is a fire-attribute martial soul of the highest grade. At over 150 years old, his combat experience is extremely rich. As the chief priest of the Spirit Hall, Sun Douluo’s overall strength surpasses all others.]

225
00:15:47,016 --> 00:16:27,816
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

